{"tid":1323796,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"知法犯法！建制派地區辦$0租","createTime":"2019-07-16T11:10:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-17T05:04:30.000Z","uid":265546,"like":25,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"13a938cc4c61bdeb4311de9690e1a3cfffd47719","tid":1323796,"uid":265546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T11:10:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DJcSRHL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDJcSRHL.jpg&h=92701eaa&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BxOOp2T.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBxOOp2T.jpg&h=353b7d35&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n建制派社區主任地辦大部分都唔洗交租！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n建制派的&ldquo;公屋聯會&rdquo;向房署申請以優惠租金租用辦事處，但不是供社團用，而是免費提供比民建聯做區內社區主任的地辦（差不多所有區都有），其實建制派不能以自己名義去租，因為房署撥左某些單位用作社團辦事處。建制係唔可以租用的，所以用社團名義去租。<br />\n房署點解唔管呢？<br />\n選舉經費又計唔計呢？<br />\n之前問過房署，佢地話管唔到，大家一齊出信比房署署長要求交代， 各自做野啦！<br />\n社團組織的門口會貼滿建制poster，大家自己去影啦！<br />\n（Share比房署商業租戶，佢地可能會嬲嬲豬，點解民建聯唔洗交租！）<br />\n公屋聯會<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.hkph.org/main/contact/sub.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkph.org%2Fmain%2Fcontact%2Fsub.html&d=FVRAyOQFEUVrsg2I2pbTeUaSLYUUk8srzc0BovwEr9s%3D&h=c619b9d3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkph.org/main/contact/sub.html</a><br />\n九龍社團聯會<br />\n<a href=\"https://klnfas.hk/tc/%E6%9C%AC%E6%9C%83%E7%B0%A1%E4%BB%8BMgvsac627ab1ccbdb62ec96e702f07f6425bZ062fddee8df90b1a0c77860a52b4d68ddoFcw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fklnfas.hk%2Ftc%2F%25E6%259C%25AC%25E6%259C%2583%25E7%25B0%25A1%25E4%25BB%258BMgvsac627ab1ccbdb62ec96e702f07f6425bZ062fddee8df90b1a0c77860a52b4d68ddoFcw&d=FVRAyOQFEUVrsg2I2pbTeUaSLYUUk8srzc0BovwEr9s%3D&h=96cb1987\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://klnfas.hk/tc/%E6%9C%AC%E6%9C%83%E7%B0%A1%E4%BB%8BMgvsac627ab1ccbdb62ec96e702f07f6425bZ062fd